The Town Lodge Waterfall is the ideal choice for travellers on a budget who want to be close to the action. Guests enjoy fast and reliable WiFi, a choice of continental or a full English breakfast, sparkling swimming pool, sundowner bar, landscaped gardens and same-day laundry and dry cleaning. Our recently launched Eat-in restaurant is now open for lunch and dinner, serving firm favourites such as our Shisa Nyama platter!Air-conditioned rooms are comfortably appointed with double or twin beds, and interleading family rooms are available, en suite bathroom with shower, television with selected DStv channels and radio stations, tea and coffee making facilities, and electronic safe. The hotel also has rooms designed to meet the needs of those living with disabilities.The Town Lodge Waterfall is located in easy reach of Waterfall City, which features the iconic Mall of Africa retail and entertainment destination, as well as a variety of corporate offices. It is close to the Gautrain Midrand station and conference venues Gallagher Convention Centre and Kyalami Exhibition Centre.Lindiwe Sangweni-Siddo says, “As central business districts (CBDs) grow and develop, we like to ensure our hotels correctly reflect a sense of place. Town Lodge Waterfall is a perfectly located property in the Waterfall precinct, and therefore it makes sense to update the name accordingly.”Find out more here, see our latest specials and discounts here.